('b2bbd809-e121-4abd-b8d7-3ddc88d8193b', 'Nordic Naturals: The Gold Standard Fish Oil', 'The #1 selling omega-3 with IFOS 5-star certification. Superior triglyceride form ensures better absorption than cheaper ethyl ester fish oils.', 'EPA (650mg) and DHA (450mg) in the natural triglyceride form. IFOS 5-star certified for purity, potency, and freshness. Friend of the Sea sustainable sourcing.', ARRAY['Natural triglyceride form', 'IFOS 5-star certified', 'No fishy aftertaste', 'Sustainable sourcing'], 'Take 2 softgels daily with food. Store in refrigerator after opening.', ARRAY['Requires 2 softgels for full dose', 'Premium pricing', 'Must refrigerate after opening'], 'Anyone wanting heart, brain, and joint health support from the most trusted omega-3 brand.', 'Vital Proteins Collagen for structural protein. CoQ10 for heart and energy.', 'Q: Triglyceride vs ethyl ester? A: Triglyceride form is up to 70% better absorbed. Q: Why no fishy burps? A: Nordic Naturals surpasses international freshness standards, preventing oxidation that causes fishy taste.', 8.8, '[{"name": "William J.", "rating": 5, "text": "The only fish oil that does not give me fishy burps. IFOS certification gives me total confidence in purity.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-08"}, {"name": "Catherine R.", "rating": 5, "text": "My cardiologist specifically recommended Nordic Naturals for the triglyceride form. My inflammation markers improved.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-21"}]'::jsonb),

('5c2e873a-acc1-4460-b649-a921b74389bf', 'BioAstin Astaxanthin: Nature''s Superantioxidant', 'Natural astaxanthin from Hawaiian microalgae is 6000x stronger than vitamin C as an antioxidant. Strong evidence for skin protection and anti-inflammatory benefits.', 'Natural Astaxanthin at 12mg from Haematococcus pluvialis microalgae grown in Hawaii. This carotenoid does not convert to vitamin A, making it safe at high doses.', ARRAY['Extremely potent antioxidant', 'Supports skin health', 'Anti-inflammatory properties', 'Sustainably grown in Hawaii'], 'Take 1 softgel daily with a fat-containing meal for optimal absorption.', ARRAY['Takes 2-4 weeks for noticeable effects', 'Can turn skin slightly orange at very high doses', 'Premium pricing'], 'Skin health seekers, outdoor athletes, and anyone wanting powerful natural anti-inflammatory support.', 'Resveratrol for polyphenol antioxidant. CoQ10 for mitochondrial energy. Collagen for structural support.', 'Q: Will it turn my skin orange? A: At 12mg daily, no. Only very high doses over extended periods might cause a slight orange tint. Q: Can it replace sunscreen? A: No, but it provides internal UV protection that complements sunscreen.', 8.2, '[{"name": "Paula G.", "rating": 5, "text": "After 6 weeks my skin looks more vibrant and my joint pain from running has decreased significantly.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-06"}, {"name": "Andrew F.", "rating": 4, "text": "Great antioxidant. As a surfer, I notice less skin damage from sun exposure since starting astaxanthin.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-18"}]'::jsonb),

('e3206745-eb8f-4103-9e4c-3e87f04f8602', 'Thorne Quercetin Phytosome: Enhanced Senolytic', 'Thorne''s phytosome technology delivers 20x better absorption. Quercetin is emerging as an important senolytic that clears damaged zombie cells.', 'Quercetin Phytosome (Quercefit) binds quercetin with sunflower phospholipids for 20x better absorption. Quercetin acts as a senolytic and supports immune and cardiovascular health.', ARRAY['20x better absorption', 'Senolytic properties', 'NSF Certified for Sport', 'Supports immune and cardiovascular health'], 'Take 1 capsule 1-2 times daily. Can be paired with fasting protocols for enhanced senolytic effect.', ARRAY['Capsule-only format', 'Premium Thorne pricing', 'Single ingredient'], 'Longevity enthusiasts interested in senolytics and clearing senescent cells for healthy aging.', 'Spermidine for autophagy. Basis for NAD+ boosting. Resveratrol for sirtuin activation.', 'Q: What are senolytics? A: Compounds that selectively clear senescent (zombie) cells that accumulate with age and drive inflammation. Q: Should I pair it with fasting? A: Some researchers suggest combining quercetin with intermittent fasting for enhanced senolytic effects.', 8.4, '[{"name": "Dr. Helen P.", "rating": 5, "text": "The phytosome technology makes a real difference in absorption. I include this in my longevity protocol.", "verified": true, "date": "2026-01-09"}, {"name": "George M.", "rating": 4, "text": "Part of my senolytic stack. Thorne quality as always and the improved absorption is noticeable.", "verified": true, "date": "2025-12-20"}]'::jsonb);